Class VisualizationFrameworkController

 @RequestMapping(value="/frameworks")
public class VisualizationFrameworkController

    A Spring controller which exposes an API for the client to upload new VisualizationFrameworks as well as perform CRUD operations on VisualizationMethod and their VisualizationFrameworks
